She smiled at seeing Technosis again. Then she heard the update.  She 
growled in her kitten growl, "Don't you worry. I'm here and I'll fight who 
ever messes with my friends. I'll turn them into sabertooth tger fodder I 
will. You can bet your astoriods on it."  She walked around all acting tough 
and trying to show that she had what it took to stand up to t full sized 
bot. Despite the fact that she was  only 3 foot tall in sabertooth tiger 
kitten mode and 3 1/2 foot in bot mode. But she had yet to change into bot 
mode yet.
"I'm here and no one will mes with anyone as long as I'm here."  She glanced 
around at everybot near her. "Right?"
